OL,3,CMan jailed after racially abusing bus
OL,4,Cdriver and attacking betting shop
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced to 10 months
OL,7,Fimprisonment after pleading guilty to
OL,8,Fracially abusing a bus driver and
OL,9,Fviolently attacking a betting shop.
OL,11,FThe first incident saw Michael Mongan,
OL,12,F39, of Castle Road, Ealing, west
OL,13,FLondon, attack a Ladbrokes branch in
OL,14,FNortholt on July 27.
OL,16,FHe repeatedly hit windows with a large
OL,17,Fstick and racially abused staff while
OL,18,Funder the influence of alcohol. A
OL,19,Fmember of the public had to restrain
OL,20,Fhim before he was arrested by police.
