OL,3,CMan jailed after racially abusing bus
OL,4,Cdriver and attacking betting shop
OL,6,FWhile in custody, Mongan racially
OL,7,Fabused a police officer who was
OL,8,Fdriving a van.
OL,10,FMongan pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,11,Fracially aggravated behaviour, one
OL,12,Fcharge of criminal damage and one
OL,13,Fcount of causing damage to a police
OL,14,Fvehicle.
OL,16,FThe second incident occurred on August
OL,17,F7, while he was on bail for the
OL,18,Fprevious offences, after a bus driver
OL,19,Frefused to let him board as he did not
OL,20,Fhave the money to pay for his journey.
