OL,3,CMan jailed after racially abusing bus
OL,4,Cdriver and attacking betting shop
OL,6,FMongan spat at the bus driver's cab a
OL,7,Fnumber of times while shouting
OL,8,FIslamophobic abuse and other threats.
OL,10,FHis lawyer, Giovanna Fiorentino, said
OL,11,FMongan had claimed a member of the
OL,12,Fpublic had offered to pay for his fare
OL,13,Fbut the bus driver was still refusing
OL,14,Fto let him board.
OL,16,FA video of the incident was widely
OL,17,Fshared on social media, and Mongan was
OL,18,Fidentified and arrested on Friday.
