OL,3,CMan jailed after racially abusing bus
OL,4,Cdriver and attacking betting shop
OL,6,FHe was charged with a racially
OL,7,Faggravated public order offence and
OL,8,Fcriminal damage.
OL,10,FHe appeared at Uxbridge Magistrates'
OL,11,FCourt on Tuesday where Judge Ian
OL,12,FComfort sentenced him to 10 months
OL,13,Fimprisonment for all charges.
OL,15,FThe sentence included four months in
OL,16,Fcustody for each of the two charges of
OL,17,Fracially aggravated behaviour, two
OL,18,Fmonths for criminal damage to
OL,19,FLadbrokes and one month for criminal
OL,20,Fdamage to a police vehicle. All
OL,21,Fcharges will run concurrently.
