OL,6,FHe was also sentenced to six months in
OL,7,Fcustody for racially abusing the bus
OL,8,Fdriver, which will run consecutively
OL,9,Fto the other sentences, and one month
OL,10,Ffor damaging the cab door of the bus,
OL,11,Fwhich will run concurrently.
OL,13,FHe was also told to pay #500 to the
OL,14,Fbus driver, #200 to the police officer
OL,15,Fhe racially abused and #200 to a staff
OL,16,Fmember at Ladbrokes.
