OL,3,CMan jailed after racially abusing bus
OL,4,Cdriver and attacking betting shop
OL,6,FSentencing, Judge Ian Comfort told him
OL,7,Fhis actions were "appalling" and said
OL,8,Fof the bus incident: "This was
OL,9,Fappalling racial and religious abuse
OL,10,Fover a sustained period of time.
OL,12,F"Your behaviour (occurred) when there
OL,13,Fwas violent disorder in other parts of
OL,14,Fthe country against Muslims and other
OL,15,Fgroups."
OL,17,FOn the Ladbrokes incident, he said:
OL,18,F"There was racially aggravated
OL,19,Fbehaviour towards staff who ... were
OL,20,Funable to escape your tirade.
